quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Hadst thou considered one who denies this way of life
  107,2,And that is he who drives away with force the orphan
  107,3,and urges not to give food to the needy
  107,4,So woe to ones who formally pray
  107,5,ones who are inattentive to their formal prayers
  107,6,those who make display
  107,7,yet they repulse giving the assistance